    dc:creator "Sasakawa, Mitsuhiro" ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "Oriental species of clusiid flies (Diptera: Clusiidae: Clusiinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205907>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205908>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205906> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205907>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 18. Male genitalia of Sobarocephala fuscifacies sp. nov. (12 – 14, holotype) and S. geniculata sp. nov. (15 – 18, holotype). See Figs 1 – 3 for explanation of parts; 14, phallus, ventral view; 18, distal part of phallus, ventral view. Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205907/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205908>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 – 24. Male genitalia of Sobarocephala megastylis sp. nov. (19 – 22, holotype) and Tetrameringia maculata sp. nov. (23, 24, paratype). See Figs 1 – 3 for explanation of parts. Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205908/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205906>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 11. Male genitalia of Sobarocephala baculigera sp. nov. (6 – 8, holotype) and S. eurystylis sp. nov. (9 – 11, holotype). See Figs 1 – 3 for explanation of parts; 7, 10, anterior view, left half, with detail of cercal armature of former. Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

